### Obtener información del servidor e inicializar el canal (Endpoint SSE)
GET http://localhost:5003/mcp

### Listar herramientas
POST http://localhost:5003/mcp/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/list"
}

### Llamar a la herramienta 'Saludar'
POST http://localhost:5003/mcp/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "Saludar",
    "arguments": {
      "nombre": "Ada Lovelace"
    }
  }
}
